<li id="cite_note-malleus-47"><b><a href="#cite_ref-malleus_47-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFSummersSprenger_.26_Kramer"><a href="/wiki/Montague_Summers" title="Montague Summers">Summers, Montague</a>; Sprenger &amp; Kramer (1484, 1971 (trans)). <i><a href="http://classiclit.about.com/library/bl-etexts/msummers/bl-msummers-vampire-3.htm" class="external text" title="http://classiclit.about.com/library/bl-etexts/msummers/bl-msummers-vampire-3.htm" rel="nofollow">Malleus Maleficarum</a></i>. pp.&#160;Ch. 3. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0486228029" class="internal">ISBN 0486228029</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://classiclit.about.com/library/bl-etexts/msummers/bl-msummers-vampire-3.htm" class="external free" title="http://classiclit.about.com/library/bl-etexts/msummers/bl-msummers-vampire-3.htm" rel="nofollow">http://classiclit.about.com/library/bl-etexts/msummers/bl-msummers-vampire-3.htm</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Malleus+Maleficarum&amp;rft.aulast=Summers&amp;rft.aufirst=Montague&amp;rft.au=Summers%2C+Montague&amp;rft.au=Sprenger+%26+Kramer&amp;rft.date=1484%2C+1971+%28trans%29&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3BCh.+3&amp;rft.isbn=0486228029&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fclassiclit.about.com%2Flibrary%2Fbl-etexts%2Fmsummers%2Fbl-msummers-vampire-3.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Red_hair"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> - see <a href="/wiki/Malleus_Maleficarum" title="Malleus Maleficarum">Malleus Maleficarum</a></li>
